17cb3587475ae9dc65ecb5","tid":2241183,"uid":43015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"810aaf3127ec47f469a51df27fbc77998b515e8c","tid":2241183,"uid":154258,"like":16,"dislike":7,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"架生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊到鄉下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%B6%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259E%25B6%25E7%2594%259F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=2b7ea3af\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%B6%E7%94%9F</a><br />\n水滸傳出版時用咗「家生」。「家生」響蘇州話指刀槍等武器，亦指器具。南昌贛語、長沙湘語（白讀）、汕頭閩語（文讀）、南雄珠璣客家話「家」字讀音接近粵語「架」文讀音；建甌閩北語「生」讀音係ʦʰaŋ（平聲），聲母、韻母、音調類及值近乎粵語 「撐」讀音。《廣州話方言字字典》引《漢語大字典》指「罉」本字係「鐺」（楚耕切），即三腳煲。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552bc3f2bea32b1e02cd76c4e75873e9e792da18","tid":2241183,"uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"但我自己聽同用都係架撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d439c389184ca7ae8188b4ad465ce58b0d76d285","tid":2241183,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"一直都係寫生<br />\n生, 生財也"},{"pid":"088ac403a14ca07adbe774ed6e501ee5bcb6c21d","tid":2241183,"uid":80455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5c0e31dadc3ff4e0365e7ef61166253881f959","tid":2241183,"uid":77368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"樓主高質喎"},{"pid":"5b2efaa1e5fa4b14b6e1a2168ef45e43d6d38ac9","tid":2241183,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"由小流氓、龍虎門開始<br />\n寫就用(架生)、平時講音讀(架撐）"},{"pid